  <brief_title>Hysteroscopy After Pretreatment With Misoprostol and Estradiol Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Self-Administered Vaginal Misoprostol Result in Cervical Ripening in Postmenopausal Women After 14 Days Pre-Treatment With Estradiol?</official_title>
