  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate whether 1000 micrograms of self-administered vaginal
      misoprostol 12 hours before operative hysteroscopy results in effective preoperative cervical
      ripening after two weeks pretreatment with 25 micrograms daily vaginal estradiol, compared to
      placebo (lactosum monohydricum) in postmenopausal women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
